  "description": "A vibrant daytime scene of San Francisco's skyline as viewed from the water. A boat is speeding away, leaving a dramatic white wake that converges toward the center of the frame. The city\u2019s buildings, varying in height and architectural style, stretch across the horizon. Prominently featured is the Transamerica Pyramid. The water is a deep blue, reflecting the clear sky and bright sunlight. The sun is a major element, appearing as a brilliant starburst at the top of the image. A metal railing is visible in the foreground, suggesting the viewpoint is from a vessel.",
